title: Dalail-ul-Khairat
description:
Dalāʼil al-khayrāt (دلائل الخيرات) is a famous collection of prayers for the Islamic prophet Muhammad SAW, which was written by the Moroccan scholar Muhammad al-Jazuli (died 1465). This video is Edited and Produced by Versatile media into video for the benefits of all caring Muslims across the world.

Versatile media did the translation into English in this video.
